    "content": "                                      Rock With You\r\n                                     Michael Jackson\r\n                                    \r\n\r\nBass                                                          Rod Temperton\r\n\r\nAs played by Bobby Watson\r\n\r\nTuning: Eb Ab Db Gb\r\n\r\nIntro\r\n\r\n1 Bar Rest\r\n\r\n[tab]Gb|-----------------|---------4-------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nDb|-----------------|-------4---4-----|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nAb|-----------------|-2-----------2---|-----------------|-2-----5-----6---|\r\nEb|-0-----0-0-------|---------------0-|-0-----0-0-------|-----------------|\r\n    E E E.S E E Q     E E E.S E.S E E   E E E.S E E Q     Q.    Q.    Q[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Gb|-----------------|---------4-------|-----------------|-------------------|\r\nDb|-----------------|-------4---4-----|-----------------|---------------0-2-|\r\nAb|-----------------|-2-----------2---|-0-----0-------0-|-0-----0---1-2-----|\r\nEb|-0-----0-0-------|---------------0-|-----------------|-------------------|\r\n    E E E.S E E Q     E E E.S E.S E E   Q.    H       E   Q.    Q   E E S S[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse 1\r\n\r\n[tab]Gb|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-------4---------|\r\nDb|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----4-------0-2-|\r\nAb|-----------------|-----------------|-2-------2-------|-2-------2-------|\r\nEb|-0-----x-3---4---|-5-----x-5---6---|-----------------|-----------------|\r\n    E E E.S Q   Q     E E E.S Q   Q     E Q.    E Q.      E E.S E E E E E[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Gb|-------------------|-----------------|-------------4---|-----------------|\r\nDb|-------------------|-----------------|-----------4-----|-------4-----2---|\r\nAb|-------------------|-----------------|-2-----2-------2-|-2-------2-0---0-|\r\nEb|-0-----x-0---x-3-4-|-5-----x-5---6---|-----------------|-----------------|\r\n    E E E.S E S S E E   E E E.S Q   Q     E Q.  E S S E.S   E Q.  E E S S E[/ta